name: Arduino-sacred-geometry
tagline: Example of how to create the flower of life in a Display Lcd Tft 1,44 128x128 Spi Nokia Arduino Pic
body:
### Arduino nano
In this project one Arduino Nano ATmega328 was used.

![arduinonano.jpg](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dilnei/Arduino-Sacred-Geometry/master/arduinonano.jpg)

### Libraries used 
* Adafruit_GFX.h
* TFT_ILI9163C.h
